'''Johann Gottlieb Christaller''' (19 Adeɛmekpɔxe 1827 - 16 Dzome 1895)<ref name="akan">[http://www.akan.org/akan_cd/ALIAKAN/course/U-References-p210.html Akan Teleteaching Course - Annex 8: Christaller] Axa sia tso:Akan.org; Wotsɔe:8  Afɔfiɛ 2018</ref> enye mawunyagblɔla, gbemeɖela tso Dzemeni si wɔ dɔ kpakple Bremen Mission hamea. Esrɔ̃ nu geɖe hã le [[Blugbe]] gbɔgblɔ ŋuti le ɣemaɣi me Gold Coast dukɔ la nɔ anyi. Enɔ amesiwo ɖe Biblia gɔme ɖe Blugbe me. Ame geɖe kpɔe abe amesi do West Afrika gbegbɔgblɔwo sɔsrɔ̃ ɖe ŋgɔ.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Jungraithmayr|first1=Hermann & Wilhelm J.G. Möhlig|url=http://www.akan.org/akan_cd/ALIAKAN/course/U-References-p211.html#Jungraithmayr%201983|title=Lexicon der Afrikanistik|date=1983|publisher=Dietrich Reimer|location=berlin|page=63|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref>

==Eƒe suku dede kple dɔ sɔsrɔ̃==
Wodzi Johann Christaller le Winnenden si medidi tso Stuttgart le Dzemeni o. Fofoa nye awutɔla. Agbalẽ xexlẽ dzɔa dzi ne Johann tɔ ŋutɔ eyata agbalẽwo sɔgbɔ ɖe esi le aƒe alegbegbe. Nusia na agbalẽ xexlẽ dzɔa dzi na Johann hã. Le suku dedevɔ megbe la, eva yi wɔ agbalẽ dɔ le Winnenden gbɔ me.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Harries|first1=Patrick|title=The Spiritual in the Secular: Missionaries and Knowledge  Africa (Studies in the History of Christian Missions)|date=30 June 2012|publisher=Wm. B. Eerdmans Publishing Company|isbn=978-0802866349|page=86|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=tVJuQbQ0UgwC&pg=PA102&lpg=PA102&dq=%22Johann+Gottlieb+Christaller%22&source=bl&ots=VpUgtdW4wp&sig=RSAdeVaqtGptbI4eRExMRyzaOxc&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiKro3ey6TaAhUUesAKHZhrCYY4ChDoAQg_MAQ#v=onepage&q=%22Johann%20Gottlieb%20Christaller%22&f=false|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref> Le esia yome la, evayi de Basel Mission Mawunaygbɔgblɔ suku si le [[Basel]] le [[Switzerland]] le Anyɔnyɔ 1948 me. Wo ɖoe osɔfo le 7 Adeɛmekpɔxe 1852.<ref name="akan"/> During his studies there, he edit the grammer of the Twi language.<ref name="dacb">{{cite web|title=Christaller, Johannes Gottlieb (A)|url=https://dacb.org/stories/ghana/christaller-j/|website=Dictionary of African Christian Biography|publisher=Centre for Global Christanity and Mission|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref>

==Dɔwɔwɔ le Ghana==
Basel Mission tɔwo ɖo Johann Christaller ɖe Ghana na woƒe dɔwɔwɔ. Esime woɖo la, eva dze [[Osu]] si le [[Gɛ̃]] le 25 Dzove 1853. Eƒe lame va gblẽ eye wò gbugbɔ zɔ mɔ yi Dzemeni le 1858 me. Egbugbɔ va Ghana le Damɛ 1862 eye wò va dze [[Aburi]].<ref name="akan"/> Le esrɔ̃a ƒe ku megbe le 1866 me la, eʋu yi [[Akropong]]. Eƒe dɔ veve tɔ ɖeka si wò wɔ le Ghana enye Bibla meɖeɖe ɖe Blugbe me. Ewɔ dɔ sia kple David Asante kple Theophilus Opoku. Dɔ sia wu nu le 1871 me. Enɔ Ghana vaseɖe 1868.<ref name="dacb"/>

==Eƒe ƒometɔwo==
Johann Christaller ɖe Christine Emilie Ziegler, amesi nye mawunyaŋu dɔwɔla bubu tso [[Waiblingen]] le Dzemeni le Dzove 1857 me. Eƒe dzilawo nye Christian Ludwig Ziegler kple Rosine Kübler. Wodzi vi atɔ̃, ŋutsuvi ene kpaple nyɔnuvi ɖeka.<ref name="dacb"/> Wo vi dometɔwoa wo etɔ̃ enye [[:de:Erdmann Gottreich Christaller|Erdmann Gottreich Christaller]], si nye mawunya gblɔla kple agbalẽŋlɔla, Theodor Benjamin Christaller, si fia nu le [[Cameroon]] sukuwo me kple Hanna Christaller, si ŋlɔ "Kolonial novellen (Togo)".<ref>{{cite web|title=Johann Gottlieb Christaller|url=https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Gottlieb_Christaller|website=German Wikipedia|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref><ref name="christine">{{cite web|title=Christiane Christaller|url=https://www.myheritage.com/names/christiane_christaller|website=MyHeritage.com|publisher=My Heritage Ltd|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref> Emilie ku le 13 Dasiamime 1866 le [[Kyebi]] le [[Akyem Abuakwa]] nutome. Egbugbɔ yi Dzemeni le 1868. Emegbe la, eɖe Bertha Ziegle, si nye Christine ƒe nɔvinyɔnu le 1872 me. Woameveawo hã dzi vi atɔ̃, ŋutsuvi ene kpakple nyɔnuvi ɖeka.<ref name="akan"/>

==Nuŋɔŋlɔwo kple dzesidedewo==
Johann ƒe agbalẽ si wo xɔ ŋkɔ wu dometɔ aɖewo wo nye ''A Grammar of the Asante and Fante Language Called Tshi (Twi, Chee) Based on the Akuapem Dialect with Reference to Other (Akan and Fante) Dialects'' si wòŋlɔ le 1875 me kple ''A Dictionary of the Asante and Fante Language Called Twi'', ISBN:978-1104592219, le 1871 me. Agbalɛ̃ eve sia wo ƒe tat gbãtɔ wo do le Basel. Institu de France tɔwo hã do dzesi le eƒe dɔwɔwɔ ta kple dzesi si woyɔna be [[Volney Prize]].<ref name="dacb"/>                         
 
==Akrofi-Christaller Institute of Theology, Mission and Culture==
Akrofi-Christaller Institute enye suku de ŋgɔ le Akropong si le abe univesiti ene. Wo doa ŋusẽ amewo be na woa srɔ̃ɔ nu le Mawunya ƒe gɔmedzedze kple kakaka ɖe Ghana kple Afrika katã. Wo tsɔ Clement Anderson Akrofi kple Johann Gottlieb Christaller ƒe ŋkɔwo na sukua.<ref>{{cite web|title=Akrofi-Christaller Institute (ACI)|url=http://www.acighana.org/site/aboutus/index.php|website=Official website|publisher=Akrofi-Christaller Institute of Theology, Mission and Culture|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref>

